{"tid":2276856,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國會列連串事例：港人權急劇惡化  政府深夜發稿狡辯","createTime":"2020-11-08T05:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:01:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3133689c92ee68cd664926aed4a0b374751b62","tid":2276856,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/UUBZWT6C45CNFASRWR2EN2B5LA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FUUBZWT6C45CNFASRWR2EN2B5LA%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft29C8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=549b09d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FUUBZWT6C45CNFASRWR2EN2B5LA%2F&h=4de4e63a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/UUBZWT6C45CNFASRWR2EN2B5LA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美國會列連串事例：港人權急劇惡化 <br />\n政府深夜發稿狡辯<br />\n<br />\n【政治熱話】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國國會及行政當局中國委員會（CECC）近日發表報告，指國安法下香港人權狀況急劇惡化。報告列舉多個事例，包括港府干預立會選舉、鎮壓支持民主人士和傳媒、律政司介入私人檢控等，顯示國安法對港影響。港府辯稱報告偏頗，抹黑國安法及香港人權狀況。<br />\n<br />\n報告以「香港人權在國安法通過後急速惡化」為題，指出港府在政治自由、集會自由、學術自由及律政司介入私人檢控等方面，無視《基本法》中的《國際公民及政治權利公約》侵害香港人權。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，港人過去多年7.1上街遊行表達訴求，但今年7.1上街被警方拘捕者共370人。另外原定今年9月舉行的立法會選舉，選舉主任不但取消12名民主派參選資格，港府更藉武漢肺炎疫情為由，將選舉押後一年。<br />\n<br />\n警方國安處7月拘捕前學生動源召集人鍾翰林，及前學生動源發言人何諾恆、。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/puOApFpuMBDU0OIHZZvC2IzxnFI=/640x460/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3AY6FFG245BFTI4UWONT7KE6FU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpuOApFpuMBDU0OIHZZvC2IzxnFI%3D%2F640x460%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3AY6FFG245BFTI4UWONT7KE6FU.jpg&h=1dec1563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國國會近日發表報告指國安法下香港人權狀況急劇惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥警搜《蘋果》鎮壓傳媒<br />\n<br />\n今年8月警方國安處連同刑事處人員大規模搜捕，以違反國安法等罪名，拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、其兩名兒子、四名壹傳媒高層及前香港眾志成員周庭等共十人，逾200名警員直闖蘋果日報大樓帶走25箱資料。報告認為，這是鎮壓爭取民主傳媒的事例。<br />\n<br />\n報告亦列出12名港人送中、。。。。。。。。。。。。，以及在深水埗鏟上行人路撞人之的士司機鄭國泉危險駕駛案。<br />\n<br />\n港府周五深夜發出新聞稿回應，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港府續稱，押後選舉基於公。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n就律政司介入私人檢控案件，港府稱《。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F9OiYuXKicZEcL1bqSoy0XTCKag=/953x1845/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TFNAHCMV7JG33IFJJHMEUYJGSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF9OiYuXKicZEcL1bqSoy0XTCKag%3D%2F953x1845%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTFNAHCMV7JG33IFJJHMEUYJGSM.jpg&h=fcdaaeec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5493d901394c74bd7d95dbb8b7b10c4469e8af0","tid":2276856,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:38:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4765e941a8cccfbf12591d01c663e274f4eff184","tid":2276856,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"美國：55"},{"pid":"0744c7ca5228b69b3c0cbfcebf275ffbf5e49446","tid":2276856,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾撚厚面皮先至講得出"},{"pid":"e1fc278a2e7f63ec2dc1706c7a216b7229435d7c","tid":2276856,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6de113281064196423f3bed2a31c97181e63bfb6","tid":2276856,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"仲想兜，好心啦盲嘅都知"}]}